{"tid":1496612,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一 名 和 理 非 的 懺 悔","createTime":"2019-08-22T15:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T15:59:46.000Z","uid":288370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e56214c2dc1be3f515ab60337c1d8941cd46e0f8","tid":1496612,"uid":288370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"Sorry咁多位，有少少標題黨feel。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個唔會點上前線，膽小怕事的和理非，明白到今日真係講幾多次sorry都無用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到前線手足被補被虐打，控訴無門，咩方法都試過晒，但五大訴求仲未有一項落實，更甚是，被秋後算帳的人愈來愈多。<br />\n<br />\n無錯，上星期日維園同港島嗰一片人海，真係令我好感動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但，當我星期一再返工時，地鐵見到的仍然係一張又一張冷漠的臉。低頭碌機的碌機，或依舊企喺車廂中間郁都唔郁，但身邊的人可能就係星期日出過嚟的手足。面對住兩個咁嘅平行時空，你話點會唔心up&mdash;&mdash;原來一到上班日子，我哋就打回原形....... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回想8月5日嗰次罷工，真係好一鼓作氣。雖然得嗰35萬人，但成效好大，好多鋪頭提早落閘。試想想，唔好話200萬人一齊罷，只要有100萬位和理非參與，罷工的威力一定更奏效！我見而家好多人都吹緊9月「持續罷工」的風，我真心覺得今次直情係我哋和理非報答被捕受傷手足的大好機會！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我由呢幾個星期開始，加入咗三幾個地區TG groups，幫手做吓文宣之餘，真係比好多素未謀面的手足感化到，真真正正相信&mdash;&mdash;「罷工就是最勇武的和理非」。<br />\n<br />\n和理非，9月一齊至少罷三日，甚至一星期，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feda02a30fe55062a444637e2138427947783e2c","tid":1496612,"uid":306045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"pishhh<br />\n<br />\n9.2全港大罷工兩星期<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e521e587a6f531c516fa38d4589fe902424bdfa8","tid":1496612,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBjf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBjf8.jpg&h=8a441805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgzvoHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgzvoHP.png&h=79a62f84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d16d0b06c82c8ef3990afb762cf6a91c78688502","tid":1496612,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"好內疚"},{"pid":"abfc12fb8ee59d8106e373baffb7ef7d6dfdee58","tid":1496612,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d16d0b06c82c8ef3990afb762cf6a91c78688502","tid":1496612,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit